          </p>
          <h4 class="pt-4 pb-6 text-sm font-black subpixel-antialiased">Endpoint URL</h4>
          <p class="pb-3">
            <span class="mb-3 text-gray-600 bg-green-100">GET: https://biblo-express.herokuapp.com/api/users</span>
          </p>
          <h4 class="pt-4 pb-6 text-sm font-black subpixel-antialiased">Request</h4>
          <table class="w-full mb-3">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2">
